"hkgmoji\" /> 同HKSP好似差好遠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T23:27:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T23:38:23.000Z","msg":"學聯個架構本身就係線性，冇權力制衡<br />\n當年有篇文講過學聯既問題：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2015/04/21/104878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2015%2F04%2F21%2F104878&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=230ccc5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2015/04/21/104878</a><br />\n<br />\n而家咁睇HKSP暫時冇乜機會會變成咁樣"},{"pid":"f7d2b8510b7afe4714a2e3567aae4d0fb671f929","tid":2330220,"uid":13428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T23:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d52543426147fa78cbd7b3fc04ea7a57ab1ae56","tid":2330220,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T23:45:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a06955818ffb72e1972d626acf6b39676e556d07","tid":2330220,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T23:46:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"85e9bdcdd13c688d514e900d0aaa2e2d0ab6a346","tid":2330220,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T23:49:50.000Z","msg":"HKSP條宣傳片<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9WMGwyaloeo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9WMGwyaloeo&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=14695d58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9WMGwyaloeo</a>"},{"pid":"856eae8a83a1d8699ff0fc81962c4e8af80222bf","tid":2330220,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite